{"tid":1558209,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[宗教文宣] 加大宣傳 棄暗投明","createTime":"2019-09-10T11:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T14:56:32.000Z","uid":1838,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"14bb5a1a56f5f8c19476801df6458aeadec77342","tid":1558209,"uid":1838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:23:42.000Z","msg":"宗教喺世界有好大嘅影響力<br />\n不論佛教 基督教<br />\n依家中共就擺明係打壓呢啲宗教<br />\n下面有幾個例子:<br />\n【打壓宗教】替宗教塑像「整容」 景區玉觀音變嫦娥<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190910/60028629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F60028629&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4a0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=bbab555f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F60028629&h=0fb4f3ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190910/60028629</a><br />\n中共打壓宗教 民眾奇招避拆觀音像整容變孔子<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190504/20670529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190504%2F20670529&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4a0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=01926cbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190504%2F20670529&h=ebfeac0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190504/20670529</a><br />\n【打壓宗教】陝西天主教堂遭強拆 被夷為平地<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190406/59457537\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190406%2F59457537&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4a0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=612a9a04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190406%2F59457537&h=51edf657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190406/59457537</a><br />\n而我想講嘅係 佛教係大陸佔大多數<br />\n佢哋好信佛 日拜夜拜 有錢冇錢都係咁 由其是<span style=\"color: red;\">福建人</span> 藍絲都係<br />\n所以希望文宣組可以加大呢方面嘅宣傳<br />\n等佢地知道佢哋支持嘅中共 打壓緊佢哋信奉嘅神明<br />\n到時佢地全部都要拜中共 贊美中共<br />\n莫講燒香拜佛 講衰啲 屎都冇份你拜<br />\n希望佢哋可以<span style=\"color: red;\">棄暗投明</span><br />\n最後想講 如果你哋信佛人士係相信有<span style=\"color: red;\">因果報應</span>嘅<br />\n我諗中共咁多可恥 獨裁嘅行事手法 一定會受到制裁<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0cd2d613036226652ce6dff4063837b08b7b29fc","tid":1558209,"uid":1838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:24:02.000Z","msg":"721 811 831"},{"pid":"1289bd118f880f260984d63b6411dac4e98a4ed9","tid":1558209,"uid":1838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:24:12.000Z","msg":"721 811 831"},{"pid":"e41896170397e7b7dc9f7c7745ef172aebbd131f","tid":1558209,"uid":1838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:24:23.000Z","msg":"721 811 831"},{"pid":"e9a8bd5bea676536ba591028b2483ac966667cf1","tid":1558209,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CFb8tFf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCFb8tFf.jpg&h=67608619&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"789e09818949b7589d06a2ae6d8d2f782498c499","tid":1558209,"uid":1838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:30:39.000Z","msg":"721 811 831"},{"pid":"1a08b9ec2ae3cb09dfb175c1c9a610aad67346f2","tid":1558209,"uid":1838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:37:00.000Z","msg":"721 811 831"},{"pid":"63186ab99466992a988f916efcaa42218ef6915d","tid":1558209,"uid":1838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:37:10.000Z","msg